      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOOM TOWN (1) was in the placings last time but prior to that produced a speedy 20.05 win over 350m at Grafton. Can measure up again if runs up to recent best times. DAYSEA'S KURT (2) got a clear run and led until the final stages when second and beaten 3 lengths (25.73) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 457m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Well-placed to take this out. GOLDSTAR SALLY (5) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at this track the following run. Can turn it around this time. CANYA ONSLAUGHT (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
